---
layout: base
title: How-Tos
description: Step-by-step kitchen how-tos — foundational moves, specialty techniques, and the small details that make food better.
permalink: /how-tos/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">

  <header class="recipe-hero">
    <span class="recipe-hero__eyebrow">Kitchen reference</span>
    <h1 class="recipe-hero__title">How-Tos</h1>
    <p class="recipe-hero__dek">Foundational moves, specialty techniques, and the small details that make food better. Every entry is a step-by-step.</p>
  </header>

  {% set howtos = collections.techniques | reverse %}
  {% if howtos.length > 0 %}
  <section style="margin-top: var(--space-10);">
    <div class="recipe-grid">
      {% for technique in howtos %}
        {% set recipe = {
          url: technique.url,
          data: {
            title: technique.data.title,
            hero: technique.data.hero,
            heroAlt: technique.data.heroAlt,
            course: technique.data.subsection,
            author: technique.data.author,
            totalTime: technique.data.totalTime,
            cuisine: technique.data.cuisine,
            difficulty: technique.data.level
          }
        } %}
        {% include "partials/recipe-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% else %}
  <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--color-ink-faint); margin-top: var(--space-8);">No how-tos yet. <a href="/submit/technique/" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Pitch one</a>.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div>

